def load_img(folder):
    images=[]
    y_label=[]
    for i in (os.listdir(folder)):
        img=cv2.imread(os.path.join(folder,i))
        img=cv2.cvtColor(img,cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)
        img=cv2.resize(img,(800,800))
        images.append(img)
        
        if folder==r"C:\Users\ombha\OneDrive\Desktop\College stuff\ML\J021noglasses":
            y_label.append(0)
        else:
            y_label.append(1)
    
    return images,y_label

def get_array(folder):
    arrays,y_label=load_img(folder)
    arrays=np.array(arrays).reshape(-1,800*800)
    y_label=np.array(y_label).reshape(-1,1)
    return arrays,y_label

Linear and Logistic Regression¶

In [59]:
def linear_reg(x,y,epochs=1000):
    m=x.shape[0]
    nx=x.shape[1]
    y=y.reshape(-1,1)
    lr=.01
    w=np.random.rand(nx+1,1)
    x0=np.ones((m,1))
    x=np.concatenate((x0,x),axis=1)
    for i in range(epochs):
        h=np.dot(x,w)
        error=h-y
        cost=np.dot(error.T,error)/2*m
        dw=np.dot(x.T,error)/m
        w=w-lr*dw
    return w

def sigmoid(z):
    s=1/(1+np.exp(-z))
    return s


def logistic_reg(x,y,epochs=1000):
    m=x.shape[0]
    nx=x.shape[1]
    y=y.reshape(-1,1)
    lr=.01
    x0=np.ones((m,1))
    w=np.random.rand(nx+1,1)
    x=np.concatenate((x0,x),axis=1)
    for i in range(epochs):
        h=sigmoid(np.dot(x,w))
        error=h-y
        loss=np.multiply(y,np.log(h))+np.multiply((1-y),np.log(1-h))
        cost=-np.sum(loss)/m
        dw=np.dot(x.T,error)/m
        w=w-lr*dw
    return w

def sigmoid(z):
    s=1/(1+np.exp(-z))
    return s
In [62]:
def leaky(z):
    s=np.maximum(0.01,z)
    return s
In [63]:
def relu(z):
    s=np.maximum(0,z)
    return s

In [66]:
def init_parameters(nx,nh1,nh2,nh3,nh4,ny):
    W1=np.random.randn(nh1,nx)*0.01
    b1=np.zeros((nh1,1))
    
    W2=np.random.randn(nh2,nh1)*0.01
    b2=np.zeros((nh2,1))
    
    W3=np.random.randn(nh3,nh2)*0.01
    b3=np.zeros((nh3,1))
    
    W4=np.random.randn(nh4,nh3)*0.01
    b4=np.zeros((nh4,1))
    
    W5=np.random.randn(ny,nh4)*0.01
    b5=np.zeros((ny,1))
    
    parameters={"W1":W1,
               "W2":W2,
               "W3":W3,
               "W4":W4,
               "W5":W5,
               "b1":b1,
               "b2":b2,
               "b3":b3,
               "b4":b4,
               "b5":b5}
    
    return parameters

Forward propagation

In [67]:
def FWD(x,y,parameters):
    W1=parameters["W1"]
    W2=parameters["W2"]
    W3=parameters["W3"]
    W4=parameters["W4"]
    W5=parameters["W5"]
    b1=parameters["b1"]
    b2=parameters["b2"]
    b3=parameters["b3"]
    b4=parameters["b4"]
    b5=parameters["b5"]
    
    Z1=np.dot(W1,x)+b1
    A1=relu(Z1)
    
    Z2=np.dot(W2,A1)+b2
    A2=relu(Z2)
    
    Z3=np.dot(W3,A2)+b3
    A3=relu(Z3)
    
    Z4=np.dot(W4,A3)+b4
    A4=leaky(Z4)
    
    Z5=np.dot(W5,A4)+b5
    A5=sigmoid(Z5)
    
    catch={"Z1":Z1,
            "Z2":Z2,
            "Z3":Z3,
            "Z4":Z4,
            "Z5":Z5,
            "A1":A1,
            "A2":A2,
            "A3":A3,
            "A4":A4,
            "A5":A5}
    
    return catch,A5
In [68]:
def cost(y,a5):
    m=y.shape[0]
    lossf=np.multiply(y,np.log(a5))+np.multiply((1-y),np.log(1-a5))
    costf=-np.sum(lossf)/m
    
    return costf

Backward prop

In [69]:
def BWD(x,y,parameters,catch):
    W1=parameters["W1"]
    W2=parameters["W2"]
    W3=parameters["W3"]
    W4=parameters["W4"]
    W5=parameters["W5"]
    
    A1=catch['A1']
    A2=catch['A2']
    A3=catch['A3']
    A4=catch['A4']
    A5=catch['A5']
    
    m=x.shape[1]
    
    dz5=A5-y
    dw5=np.dot(dz5,A4.T)/m
    db5=np.sum(dz5,keepdims=True,axis=1)/m
    
    dz4=np.dot(W5.T,dz5)*np.where(A4>0,1,0.01)
    dw4=np.dot(dz4,A3.T)/m
    db4=np.sum(dz4,keepdims=True,axis=1)/m
    
    dz3=np.dot(W4.T,dz4)*np.where(A3>0,1,0)
    dw3=np.dot(dz3,A2.T)/m
    db3=np.sum(dz3,keepdims=True,axis=1)/m
    
    dz2=np.dot(W3.T,dz3)*np.where(A2>0,1,0)
    dw2=np.dot(dz2,A1.T)/m
    db2=np.sum(dz2,keepdims=True,axis=1)/m
    
    dz1=np.dot(W2.T,dz2)*np.where(A1>0,1,0)
    dw1=np.dot(dz1,x.T)/m
    db1=np.sum(dz1,keepdims=True,axis=1)/m
    
    grad={"dz5":dz5,"dw5":dw5,"db5":db5,
           "dz4":dz4,"dw4":dw4,"db4":db4,
           "dz3":dz3,"dw3":dw3,"db3":db3,
           "dz2":dz2,"dw2":dw2,"db2":db2,
           "dz1":dz1,"dw1":dw1,"db1":db1}
    
    return grad
In [70]:
def update(grad,parameters,lr=0.01):
    W1=parameters['W1']
    W2=parameters['W2']
    W3=parameters['W3']
    W4=parameters['W4']
    W5=parameters['W5']
    
    b1=parameters['b1']
    b2=parameters['b2']
    b3=parameters['b3']
    b4=parameters['b4']
    b5=parameters['b5']
    
    dw1=grad['dw1']
    dw2=grad['dw2']
    dw3=grad['dw3']
    dw4=grad['dw4']
    dw5=grad['dw5']
    
    db1=grad['db1']
    db2=grad['db2']
    db3=grad['db3']
    db4=grad['db4']
    db5=grad['db5']
    
    W1=W1-lr*dw1
    W2=W2-lr*dw2
    W3=W3-lr*dw3
    W4=W4-lr*dw4
    W5=W5-lr*dw5
    
    b1=b1-lr*db1
    b2=b2-lr*db2
    b3=b3-lr*db3
    b4=b4-lr*db4
    b5=b5-lr*db5
    
    parameters={"W1":W1,
               "W2":W2,
               "W3":W3,
               "W4":W4,
               "W5":W5,
               "b1":b1,
               "b2":b2,
               "b3":b3,
               "b4":b4,
               "b5":b5}
    
    return parameters
In [71]:
def NN(X,Y,itr=1000,print_cost=False):
    (nx,nh1,nh2,nh3,nh4,ny)=layers(X,Y)
    parameters=init_parameters(nx,nh1,nh2,nh3,nh4,ny)
    
    for i in range(itr):
        catch,A5=FWD(X,Y,parameters)
        costf=cost(Y,A5)
        grad=BWD(X,Y,parameters,catch)
        paras=update(grad,parameters)
        if print_cost==True:
            print(costf)

def layers1(x,y):
    nx=x.shape[0]
    nh1=4 #tanh
    nh2=2 #leakyrelu
    ny=y.shape[0] #sigmoid
    
    return nx,nh1,nh2,ny
In [74]:
def init_parameters1(nx,nh1,nh2,ny):
    W1=np.random.randn(nh1,nx)*0.01
    b1=np.zeros((nh1,1))
    
    W2=np.random.randn(nh2,nh1)*0.01
    b2=np.zeros((nh2,1))
    
    W3=np.random.randn(ny,nh2)*0.01
    b3=np.zeros((ny,1))
    
    parameters={"W1":W1,"b1":b1,
               "W2":W2,"b2":b2,
               "W3":W3,"b3":b3}
    
    return parameters
In [75]:
def FWD1(x,y,parameters):
    W1=parameters['W1']
    b1=parameters['b1']
    W2=parameters['W2']
    b2=parameters['b2']
    W3=parameters['W3']
    b3=parameters['b3']
    
    Z1=np.dot(W1,x)+b1
    A1=np.tanh(Z1)
    
    Z2=np.dot(W2,A1)+b2
    A2=leaky(Z2)
    
    Z3=np.dot(W3,A2)+b3
    A3=sigmoid(Z3)
    
    catch={"Z1":Z1,
           "Z2":Z2,
           "Z3":Z3,
           "A1":A1,
           "A2":A2,
           "A3":A3}
    
    return catch,A3
In [76]:
def cost1(A3,Y):
    m=Y.shape[1]
    loss=np.multiply(Y,np.log(A3))+np.multiply((1-Y),np.log(1-A3))
    costf=-np.sum(loss)/m
#     cost=np.squeeze(cost)
    
    return costf
In [77]:
def BWD1(X,Y,parameters,catch):
    W1=parameters['W1']
    W2=parameters['W2']
    W3=parameters['W3']
    
    Z1=catch['Z1']
    Z2=catch['Z2']
    Z3=catch['Z3']
    A1=catch['A1']
    A2=catch['A2']
    A3=catch['A3']
    
    m=X.shape[1]
    
    dz3=A3-Y
    dw3=np.dot(dz3,A2.T)/m
    db3=np.sum(dz3,keepdims=True,axis=1)/m
    
    dz2=np.dot(W3.T,dz3)*np.where(A2>0,1,0.01)
    dw2=np.dot(dz2,A1.T)/m
    db2=np.sum(dz2,keepdims=True,axis=1)/m
    
    dz1=np.dot(W2.T,dz2)*(1-A1**2)
    dw1=np.dot(dz1,X.T)/m
    db1=np.sum(dz1,keepdims=True,axis=1)/m
    
    gradients={"dz3":dz3,"dw3":dw3,"db3":db3,
              "dz2":dz2,"dw2":dw2,"db2":db2,
              "dz1":dz1,"dw1":dw1,"db1":db1}
    
    return gradients
In [78]:
def update1(gradients,parameters,lr=0.01):
    W1=parameters['W1']
    b1=parameters['b1']
    W2=parameters['W2']
    b2=parameters['b2']
    W3=parameters['W3']
    b3=parameters['b3']
    
    dz3=gradients['dz3']
    db3=gradients['db3']
    dw3=gradients['dw3']
    
    dz2=gradients['dz2']
    db2=gradients['db2']
    dw2=gradients['dw2']
    
    dz1=gradients['dz1']
    db1=gradients['db1']
    dw1=gradients['dw1']
    
    W1=W1-lr*dw1
    W2=W2-lr*dw2
    W3=W3-lr*dw3
    
    b3=b3-lr*db3
    b2=b2-lr*db2
    b1=b1-lr*db1
    
    parameters={"W1":W1,"b1":b1,
               "W2":W2,"b2":b2,
               "W3":W3,"b3":b3}
    
    return parameters

def NN1(X,Y,itr=1000,print_cost=False):
    nx,nh1,nh2,ny=layers1(X,Y)
    parameters=init_parameters1(nx,nh1,nh2,ny)
    
    for i in range(itr):
        catch,A3=FWD1(X,Y,parameters)
        costf=cost1(A3,Y)
        grads=BWD1(X,Y,parameters,catch)
        paras=update1(grads,parameters)
        
        if print_cost==True:
            print(costf)
